## ğŸ“‹ Overview

This repository provides a comprehensive survey of Indirect Immunofluorescence (IIF) HEp-2 cell image classification techniques, focusing on developments from 2012 to 2024. The survey covers traditional machine learning approaches through to state-of-the-art deep learning methods, offering insights into datasets, methodologies, and performance metrics.

