## ğŸ¯ Introduction

HEp-2 (Human Epithelial type 2) cell pattern classification is crucial for diagnosing autoimmune diseases through Antinuclear Antibody (ANA) testing. This survey aims to:

- Track the evolution of classification methods
- Compare performance metrics across different approaches
- Identify trends and challenges in the field
- Provide insights into future research directions

## ğŸ“… Research Timeline

Our survey covers three main eras:
- Traditional Machine Learning (2012-2015)
- Early Deep Learning (2015-2017)
- Advanced Deep Learning & Current SOTA (2018-2024)

## ğŸ’¾ Datasets

Detailed analysis of major HEp-2 datasets:

| Dataset | Year | Images | Classes | Usage |
|---------|------|---------|----------|--------|
| MIVIA | 2012 | 1,527 | 6 | Training/Testing |
| ICPR | 2012 | 721 | 6 | Benchmarking |
| I3A | 2014 | 20,596 | 7 | Competition |
| SNPHEp-2 | 2015 | 1,884 | 40+ | Research |

